{"tid":2132296,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"140人入院難有事打熱線  八人已等六日 醫管局促諒解","createTime":"2020-07-30T09:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T10:23:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c3871e5866ea0efcd81bbe9ad51b844772ddcbb4","tid":2132296,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T09:58:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200730/34YFZC6N3NKWMO24SBMSPY4G6A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200730%2F34YFZC6N3NKWMO24SBMSPY4G6A%2F&d=PqSGdtEI7oeKzC3efZxDSt9AtAt3lYzSqFOpIRNeugk%3D&h=1e81d929\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200730%2F34YFZC6N3NKWMO24SBMSPY4G6A%2F&h=c7bb12c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200730/34YFZC6N3NKWMO24SBMSPY4G6A/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n140人入院難有事打熱線 <br />\n八人已等六日 醫管局促諒解<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YIQGcdiwl6P_ieh3lIYvqTC-nkw=/190x128/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5CQ6KITLMMZCJCVLJOX4O5WBR4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYIQGcdiwl6P_ieh3lIYvqTC-nkw%3D%2F190x128%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5CQ6KITLMMZCJCVLJOX4O5WBR4.jpg&h=6a3baaf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何婉霞（右）昨指仍有不少病人未入院，盼市民諒解 ；左為張竹君。<br />\n<br />\n【武肺再爆發】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】公立醫院負壓病床持續爆滿，連續多日有逾百名確診病人等候入院。醫管局稱明白病人心急及無助，今日起設立新的電話專線，為等候入院病人提供資料；東區醫院亦會實施過渡安排，將一線隔離病房中的兩個病格劃作篩查病人，轉去鯉魚門社區隔離設施，直至亞博館的社區治療設施投入服務。<br />\n<br />\n截至昨日，有140名確診病人等待入院，當中八人早於7月24日確診，意味等候了六日。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n東院隔離病房病格供篩查<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：林鄭神邏輯 搞「社區飯堂」 議員：政府會堂病毒不侵？<br />\n<br />\n她又指明白在家中等待的病人心急、無助，故抽調部份原為出院病人提供支援的電話專線「護訊鈴」同事，今日起主動聯絡等入院病人，提供健康資訊、入院前須知、感染控制事項，亦會留電話予病人，一旦病人有緊急需要，可聯絡醫管局。她再次致歉：「我哋理解病人在等待嘅時候會好心急，都要講聲唔好意思，要你哋喺度等。」強調會盡快。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局最新的負壓病床及病房最新使用率分別達74.8%及86%，臨近爆滿。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n東區醫院亦設有新過渡安排，將一個一線隔離病房內的其中兩個病格劃作篩查病。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n亞博館最快周六啟用分流<br />\n<br />\n至於亞博館料最快周六啟用，何說現已做進入最後預備階段，首階段可容納逾百人，正招募醫護、支援職系同事及文職人員，同事反應正面，醫管局今日召開記者會交代詳情。另外。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"97a65cc2eb5c690554f2654fb29ff5884b284fc8","tid":2132296,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T09:59:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f62463f12c216b8eae2a79f75553dcd558bd5a0c","tid":2132296,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:00:39.000Z","msg":"Rl<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e696a24975b0ec7d11190945679a38dba298b368","tid":2132296,"uid":317378,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:02:37.000Z","msg":"其實點解隔離病房未爆滿但唔比人入去？"},{"pid":"5eb8d1a34a58d52b83823c738b51c4693d7026d0","tid":2132296,"uid":118647,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:03:24.000Z","msg":"點解唔自己去急症室？"},{"pid":"3eb80c0ef1cdf9f1d6069afd3a31505c9ff5550e","tid":2132296,"uid":48679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e696a24975b0ec7d11190945679a38dba298b368","tid":2132296,"uid":317378,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:02:37.000Z","msg":"其實點解隔離病房未爆滿但唔比人入去？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:06:51.000Z","msg":"講左十萬次<br />\n果D 係兒科,ICU, 孕婦病房黎, 根本用唔到<br />\n佢地撈埋落去做分母,扮唔係100%"},{"pid":"10226d26fda2141b880d81a429b025b445f940aa","tid":2132296,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:12:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac